messages.templateId: Hey, merc, you are just in time, you are exactly who I need. Take a VPO 208 .366 rifle and some ammo. This place became a real nasty place, its horrible. You need to clean this shit up there are a ton of fucking rats called scavs roaming around. Kill some of them using the VPO 208 rifle and come back to me for a reward....

Hey solider, I have a new mission for you, Here's the deal, I need you to take some scavs on Customs using a Molot VPO-215 Rifle so you get used to it. After this come back and I will give you some modified versions of the gun to test out and perhaps some differenet attachaments...? Anyway I need you to kill some scavs from a distance of 60 meters or something about that, get a scope or something perhaps? Good luck
Hm. You got the job done here is your reward. Come back for more jobs and rewards...

You're back? Great, I have another mission for you this time a bit different I would say. I need you to pickup me flashdrive that is located in Customs. To be more exact the location is on a table in the checkpoint tower at the military checkpoint. Be careful there might be fucking rat scavs guarding that zone... Kill them all
